Retrospective Cohort Study of Outcomes for Neonates Undergoing Inguinal Hernia Surgery at Multiple Australian and New Zealand Hospitals: The RetroNeo Neonatal Subgroup Study.

Statistical Analysis

Author

Dr Benjamin Moran, MBBS, BMedSci (Hons), MMedStats, FCICM, FANZCA

Published

March 15, 2025

1 Introduction

This is the statistical analysis that is a subgroup analysis of neonates < 28 weeks who participated in the RetroNeo study, which examines the anaesthetic techniques and perioperative outcomes of neonates and infants undergoing inguinal hernia surgery.
